{
  "sn7.6:0.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7 ",
  "sn7.6:0.2": "1. Arahantavagga ",
  "sn7.6:0.3": "6. Jaṭāsutta ",
  "sn7.6:1.1": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
  "sn7.6:1.2": "Atha kho jaṭābhāradvājo brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. ",
  "sn7.6:1.3": "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. ",
  "sn7.6:1.4": "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho jaṭābhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: ",
  "sn7.6:2.1": "“Antojaṭā bahijaṭā, ",
  "sn7.6:2.2": "Jaṭāya jaṭitā pajā; ",
  "sn7.6:2.3": "Taṃ taṃ gotama pucchāmi, ",
  "sn7.6:2.4": "Ko imaṃ vijaṭaye jaṭan”ti. ",
  "sn7.6:3.1": "“Sīle patiṭṭhāya naro sapañño, ",
  "sn7.6:3.2": "Cittaṃ paññañca bhāvayaṃ; ",
  "sn7.6:3.3": "Ātāpī nipako bhikkhu, ",
  "sn7.6:3.4": "So imaṃ vijaṭaye jaṭaṃ. ",
  "sn7.6:4.1": "Yesaṃ rāgo ca doso ca, ",
  "sn7.6:4.2": "avijjā ca virājitā; ",
  "sn7.6:4.3": "Khīṇāsavā arahanto, ",
  "sn7.6:4.4": "tesaṃ vijaṭitā jaṭā. ",
  "sn7.6:5.1": "Yattha nāmañca rūpañca, ",
  "sn7.6:5.2": "asesaṃ uparujjhati; ",
  "sn7.6:5.3": "Paṭighaṃ rūpasaññā ca, ",
  "sn7.6:5.4": "etthesā chijjate jaṭā”ti. ",
  "sn7.6:6.1": "Evaṃ vutte, jaṭābhāradvājo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
  "sn7.6:6.2": "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama …pe… ",
  "sn7.6:6.3": "aññataro ca panāyasmā bhāradvājo arahataṃ ahosī”ti. "
}